# Web3 Safety — `actions`

For web3 and contract-integration work, follow `senior-coding-actions` as the source of truth:
[.cursor/skills/senior-coding-actions/SKILL.md](mdc:.cursor/skills/senior-coding-actions/SKILL.md)

## Hard stops

Stop and ask the user before continuing if any of these would be violated:
- ABI is authored inline in TypeScript instead of JSON.
- On-chain write skips `estimateGas` preflight without a documented wallet limitation.
- New read is added as standalone call even though it belongs in an existing multicall flow.
- New comments or user-facing web3 copy are written in a language other than English.
